results.title: B'day special: Taya (Naseeruddin Shah) would answer all my questions, since my father had no patience! - Om Puri's son Ishaan Puri: Exclusive!
results.description: Ishaan told us, "Naseer taya has been someone I love and adore greatly... I feel my father's presence when I interact with him... We may not speak everyday but everytime we do meet, I am reminded of my father... If there is anyone I look up to apart from my father, it is Naseer taya. He was my father's bestfriend and like a brother to him. In fact both maintained that they were closer to each other than their own brothers."
